      "source": [
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "## Key Takeaways from Visualizations\n",
        "\n",
        "✓ **Uncertainty grows over time**: Confidence bands expand (mean reversion absent in Dothan)  \n",
        "✓ **Higher volatility → Higher prices**: Convexity creates value from uncertainty  \n",
        "✓ **Long bonds more sensitive**: Steeper price decay with maturity  \n",
        "✓ **Non-normal tail risks**: Portfolio losses have heavy left tail  \n",
        "✓ **Duration dominates for small shocks, convexity for large shocks**  \n",
        "\n",
        "All these visualizations help communicate risk to stakeholders and guide decision-making!"
      ],
